            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred</p><p>Cut 1 slices of <strong>tomato </strong>per person, then dice the<strong> remaining tomato</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> in a large bowl – this is your <strong>salad dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
