      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is done, transfer to a clean board and shred it apart, using two forks – this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p><p>Season the <strong>pulled chicken</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
